<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="14Jul1937"><font color="red">14 July 1937</font> <i>Selected Letters</i> (to C.P. Curran): My pen is charged with gore because the work on the proofs of Pts I and III of <i>W i P</i> is now so involved that I have to recur to my old habit of coloured inks and pencil &hellip;  </div>
